channel.title: Need Coder for a 317 - For Co-Owner
channel.description:
[center][b][u]Project-Delta[/u][/b][/center]
[center][b]I need a coder for my new server that i made. It is prety hard to find all the Source and client files so i was wandering if there was any experienced coders out there that could help, They will get Co-Owner as a reward![/b][/center]
[ul][li]Change The client background and name[/li] [li]Change the IP that people connect to[/li] [li]Add additional Shops and Fetures[/li][/ul]
Thanks, Jack

item.title: Need Coder for a 317 - For Co-Owner
item.dc:creator: @kihomura Kihomura
item.description:
@kihomura wrote:

You should listen to people when they tell you to read the rules, not retaliate. Requesting is not allowed on these forums. You can start a development team in the development teams section if you planning on teaming up with a bunch of people to create a server, not just ask other people to do the work for you.
